{"tid":1362621,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【電音舞曲REMIX】《何家仆街何家猜》（feat. 何君堯）原：何家公雞何家猜","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T12:11:59.000Z","uid":260946,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a90a6bbc7cc2a0f25b087f450c10a2b69b9f24a2","tid":1362621,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/joseph-chan-214793743/feat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjoseph-chan-214793743%2Ffeat&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=0a9a1004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/joseph-chan-214793743/feat</a><br />\n各位巴打絲打好，輕鬆埋最後今日又要作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩日見到有巴打留言話想聽何家仆街舞曲版，心血來潮做咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n加上琴日睇埋何生段片覺得佢俾人咁搞實在戥佢唔抵，決定幫佢加條獨白落首歌度，譴責下牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n悲傷的獨白、輕快的音樂，再配上Mean大哥跳脫的唱腔帶俾耳朵超現實的衝擊！小弟第一次做電音歌，希望大家路過肯聽下，727可以一齊唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《何家仆街何家猜》（feat. 何君堯）<br />\n<br />\n主唱：Mean (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/meanHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FmeanHK%2F&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=20da26db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/meanHK/</a>) (with 何君堯獨白)<br />\n填詞：Mean<br />\nRemix: 樂古樂古<br />\n原曲：何家公雞何家猜<br />\n作曲：兒歌 / 韋然<br />\n<br />\n啊真怪誕啊又有趣 你望望龕塚裏<br />\n有伯母副屍骨咯咯咯 是何家的親生母<br />\n啊真怪誕啊又有趣 你望望龕塚裏<br />\n有伯母副屍骨咯咯咯 是何家的親生母<br />\n<br />\n何家仆街何家猜 何家子孫何仆街<br />\n何家仆街何家猜 何家母親墳倒了<br />\n南邊叔父何先生 同班黑幫(黑警)齊嘻哈<br />\n酬金不足煩媽媽 娘親墳起了<br />\n<br />\n何家仆街何家猜 何家子孫何仆街<br />\n何家仆街何家猜 何家母親墳倒了<br />\n南邊叔父何先生 同班黑幫(黑警)齊嘻哈<br />\n酬金不足煩媽媽 娘親墳起了<br />\n<br />\n(真怪 咯咯咯 啊真怪 娘親墳起了)<br />\n(啊真怪 又有趣  娘親墳起墳起墳起)"},{"pid":"a2d76d70febd4b8695786dbd04dfb63ccdb9613d","tid":1362621,"uid":216780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae8f354e233a4fa87eb9ad37ab641cdadec477b","tid":1362621,"uid":4237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11bb016aed1afcd1f4b3775eb817a300800ec39","tid":1362621,"uid":260946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"獨白都執埋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前奏<br />\n<br />\n牛屎佬 你係個人渣 <br />\n你就係罪惡嘅源頭<br />\n今日你將我父母嘅冇被打爛<br />\n呢啲係咩人咩質素<br />\n嗰種面孔突然之間<br />\n由笑容好似係無害好似係友善嘅<br />\n180度嗰種兇殘 凸起隻眼 四白眼<br />\n你會唔會上嚟我老豆老母度鞠翻個躬<br />\n如果你肯去做的話<br />\n我可以代表我全家人 原諒你<br />\n懸崖勒馬 放下屠刀<br />\n你回頭是岸啦<br />\n<br />\n結尾<br />\n<br />\n今日係好憤怒<br />\n但係我呢個憤怒起上嚟<br />\n比起離開RTHK嘅時候呢<br />\n憤怒一萬倍都唔止<br />\n但我唔需要拍枱<br />\n但我會義正嚴詞話俾你聽<br />\n前面條路<br />\n一條係生路<br />\n另一條 係不生路<br />\n你選擇嘅係邊條啊<br />\n你慢慢諗下啦<br />\n早抖"},{"pid":"67f0c98aa37d7cdae0a458a539a4938c4bd9d909","tid":1362621,"uid":128309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"